    "English": "A data storage lattice containing a single <span class=\"name name-technology\">ByteBeat music track</span>.<br><br>Track data will be added to the 'Other Tracks' section of the <span class=\"name name-technology\">ByteBeat Library</span>. Access the Library from the Utilities section of the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
